rows.label: bf05260100_0010
rows.name: Whew, it's cold this morning...

rows.label: bf05260100_0020
rows.name: Fan-san...?

rows.label: bf05260100_0030
rows.name: Oho, has somebody got a little crush?

rows.label: bf05260100_0040
rows.name: Nia!!! What are you doing here?!

rows.label: bf05260100_0050
rows.name: Early riser. Always have been.

rows.label: bf05260100_0060
rows.name:
Ooh, I see how it is here. I wonder what
Homura and Hikari would think...

rows.label: bf05260100_0070
rows.name:
Hey, no - you've got the wrong-
Just-

rows.label: bf05260100_0080
rows.name: Just what? Go on!

rows.label: bf05260100_0090
rows.name: I dunno. I thought she looked...sad.

rows.label: bf05260100_0100
rows.name:
Oh? Rex-sama, Nia-sama.
There's still some time before your audience.

rows.label: bf05260100_0110
rows.name: Sorry, we just woke up really early.

rows.label: bf05260100_0120
rows.name: Ah, I see.

rows.label: bf05260100_0130
rows.name: That's a pretty nice mural. Very...grand.

rows.label: bf05260100_0140
rows.name: It depicts the creation of Alst.

rows.label: bf05260100_0150
rows.name:
They say this mural was painted long ago,
when the nation of Acedia was still new.

rows.label: bf05260100_0160
rows.name: You've been looking at it for a while...

rows.label: bf05260100_0170
rows.name: ...They're missing.

rows.label: bf05260100_0180
rows.name: What do you mean by "they"?

rows.label: bf05260100_0190
rows.name: My memories.

rows.label: bf05260100_0200
rows.name:
I know that I must have been around since
this mural was first painted, or even earlier, but...

rows.label: bf05260100_0210
rows.name: I don't remember that time at all.

rows.label: bf05260100_0220
rows.name: ...Well, you are a Blade.

rows.label: bf05260100_0230
rows.name: I don't know who I was or what I did.

rows.label: bf05260100_0240
rows.name: And I'd really like to.

rows.label: bf05260100_0250
rows.name:
Hikari's lived for an awful long time. Maybe
she'll know something about you.

rows.label: bf05260100_0260
rows.name: Hikari-sama called me Kasumi earlier.

rows.label: bf05260100_0270
rows.name:
Could it be possible that she met me somewhere before?
Sometime in the past?

rows.label: bf05260100_0280
rows.name: Do you wanna ask her later?

rows.label: bf05260100_0290
rows.name:
Could I? Thank you very much, 
Rex-sama.

rows.label: bf05260100_0300
rows.name:
N-no need to thank me.
You helped us too!

rows.label: bf05260100_0310
rows.name:
Look at you, going all red.
I'll tell Homura, I swear.

rows.label: bf05260100_0320
rows.name: Wha-?! I told you, it's not like that!

rows.label: bf05260100_0330
rows.name: We'll see...
